{
  "stem": "6258.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I realized that once you lost this inner discipline, really, inner discipline, get up, get washed, no matter how incredible situation, try to keep normal life and normal values.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stick to this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was Russian bread, and a piece of margarine or a sausage, soup, something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was working with these files.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Regular sleep.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At 10:00 we were in bed, and we got up at 6:00.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, we were going to roll call.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Roll call was in the morning and roll call was in the evening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were hardly inside the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the barrack was spotless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not barrack-- the block.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's still there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That block was spotless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother, when she was with me, she just put on me the blanket and told me to go out in the evening for a few minutes so that the bedding can air.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody took this from us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only holiday which could be at this time was Hanukkah, but nobody was doing this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Especially we had day, because every day they came-- papers from [GERMAN] or from the scribe, that everybody is-- so many and so many people working this kommando, or so many and so many people were [GERMAN], because they were still gassing people, but not in the big transports.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then on 18th of January, we were chased away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then suddenly, we arrived eventually in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Ravensbruck, I remember very little, except at the beginning dragging the dead people from there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I got typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No medical attention.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not everybody died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was out of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was in fever.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
